CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Flash Newspicture Magazine, November 1, 1938, pg. 11, reads: "Throughout the county the Young Men's Christian Association is launching drives to increase the membership of their association. In Pittsburg [sic] PA.,.. "
TitMainTitle: Man, possibly Everett Utterback, holding trophy, for YMCA membership drive, in Centre Avenue YMCA
